{"data":[{"id":561235130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4e2751f31a17807f658da78930dfdd77","url_token":"gao-ge-chui-zi-66","name":"红烧鱼","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35040ea5b5005a5e07f2c60b9abe35e4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35040ea5b5005a5e07f2c60b9abe35e4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4e2751f31a17807f658da78930dfdd77","user_type":"people","headline":"从前有个人，很懒","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":2,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561235130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545929917,"updated_time":1545965856,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e只要这个高中生想去就能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e既然问题开脑洞了，那就接着脑洞畅想下去…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，一个天才高中生在某期刊或者会议发表证明了“哥”的过程并被认可，然后全世界各大主流媒体轰炸式报道。第一批找上该天才的是记者，但是短暂的采访很快就会被打断，省市级领导的会面预约会被优先安排。领导向你保证家乡会给其最高的待遇，要求其保证就在地方科研相关机构。正教授是肯定的了，行政级别不太了解，说不定能直接入党，然后提拔到副处(也就是副院长)什么的。当天晚上就会受到国内各大高校终身教授的offer，当然包括清北，短信狂轰滥炸的一晚，包括之间互相爆料的内幕。如果这哥们不是北京人，几天之内就会受到中央领导人接见，提出的条件应该是清北的正教授，会有很好的行政级别，薪酬不一定能高过地方。让你保证一定要留在国内，这次不仅仅是利诱，很有可能伴随着威逼。和中央同一时间来的，还应该有世界各大名校的offer，大部分的国家提出的应该是巨额的薪酬，但像美俄这种强硬派，很有可能会有高级别人物邀约其举家移民，这时的利益很有可能让一个普通人烧坏脑子，然后答应其中一方的请求。看在少年天才的分上，没得到这哥们的势力，无论哪一国都会觉得留他不得。如果选择留在国内会被严格保护，但依然会经常有各种行刺手段。如果一念之差蒙了心答应国外，中国是绝对不会放人的，逮捕软禁是必须的，然后多国向中国施压要求放人，再接下来就是大国博弈了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实这个脑洞最恐怖的地方不仅仅在于“哥”，而在于“高二“，要是个垂暮之人也就不说什么了，一辈子呕心沥血，即便天才至极，大限将至，几乎也就没什么剩余发挥空间了，但是一个十来岁的人，解决了数以百万计的精英束手无策的问题，给他几十年，鬼tm知道这哥们能整出多大一片天。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"只要这个高中生想去就能。既然问题开脑洞了，那就接着脑洞畅想下去…首先，一个天才高中生在某期刊或者会议发表证明了“哥”的过程并被认可，然后全世界各大主流媒体轰炸式报道。第一批找上该天才的是记者，但是短暂的采访很快就会被打断，省市级领导的会面…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=467\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_a